{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1097,"text":"It was April, last year."},{"time":3714,"text":"I was on an evening out with friends"},{"time":5485,"text":"to celebrate one of their birthdays."},{"time":7677,"text":"We hadn't been all together\nfor a couple of weeks;"},{"time":10094,"text":"it was a perfect evening,\nas we were all reunited."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13220,"text":"At the end of the evening,"},{"time":14497,"text":"I caught the last underground train\nback to the other side of London."},{"time":18663,"text":"The journey was smooth."},{"time":20479,"text":"I got back to my local station"},{"time":22011,"text":"and I began the 10-minute walk home."},{"time":25159,"text":"As I turned the corner onto my street,"},{"time":27547,"text":"my house in sight up ahead,"},{"time":29596,"text":"I heard footsteps behind me"},{"time":31004,"text":"that seemed to have\napproached out of nowhere"},{"time":33191,"text":"and were picking up pace."},{"time":35778,"text":"Before I had time to process\nwhat was happening,"},{"time":38329,"text":"a hand was clapped around my mouth\nso that I could not breathe,"},{"time":41484,"text":"and the young man behind me\ndragged me to the ground,"},{"time":44208,"text":"beat my head repeatedly\nagainst the pavement"},{"time":46358,"text":"until my face began to bleed,"},{"time":48364,"text":"kicking me in the back and neck"},{"time":50596,"text":"while he began to assault me,"},{"time":52272,"text":"ripping off my clothes\nand telling me to \"shut up,\""},{"time":54758,"text":"as I struggled to cry for help."},{"time":57423,"text":"With each smack of my head\nto the concrete ground,"},{"time":59843,"text":"a question echoed through my mind\nthat still haunts me today:"},{"time":63118,"text":"\"Is this going to be how it all ends?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":66828,"text":"Little could I have realized,\nI'd been followed the whole way"},{"time":69764,"text":"from the moment I left the station."},{"time":71739,"text":"And hours later,"},{"time":72966,"text":"I was standing topless and barelegged\nin front of the police,"},{"time":76534,"text":"having the cuts and bruises\non my naked body photographed"},{"time":79330,"text":"for forensic evidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81956,"text":"Now, there are few words to describe\nthe all-consuming feelings"},{"time":85219,"text":"of vulnerability, shame, upset\nand injustice that I was ridden with"},{"time":88448,"text":"in that moment and for the weeks to come."},{"time":91868,"text":"But wanting to find a way\nto condense these feelings"},{"time":94516,"text":"into something ordered\nthat I could work through,"},{"time":96862,"text":"I decided to do what\nfelt most natural to me:"},{"time":99322,"text":"I wrote about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101149,"text":"It started out as a cathartic exercise."},{"time":103606,"text":"I wrote a letter to my assaulter,"},{"time":106688,"text":"humanizing him as \"you,\""},{"time":108807,"text":"to identify him as part\nof the very community"},{"time":111708,"text":"that he had so violently\nabused that night."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114991,"text":"Stressing the tidal-wave\neffect of his actions,"},{"time":117289,"text":"I wrote:"},{"time":118920,"text":"\"Did you ever think\nof the people in your life?"},{"time":121841,"text":"I don't know who the people\nin your life are."},{"time":124202,"text":"I don't know anything about you."},{"time":126183,"text":"But I do know this:"},{"time":127839,"text":"you did not just attack me that night."},{"time":130323,"text":"I'm a daughter, I'm a friend,"},{"time":131860,"text":"I'm a sister, I'm a pupil,"},{"time":133569,"text":"I'm a cousin, I'm a niece,"},{"time":134895,"text":"I'm a neighbor;"},{"time":136086,"text":"I'm the employee\nwho served everyone coffee"},{"time":138159,"text":"in the caf√© under the railway."},{"time":140362,"text":"And all the people who form\nthese relations to me"},{"time":142872,"text":"make up my community."},{"time":144549,"text":"And you assaulted\nevery single one of them."},{"time":147418,"text":"You violated the truth that I\nwill never cease to fight for,"},{"time":150278,"text":"and which all of these people represent:"},{"time":152239,"text":"that there are infinitely more\ngood people in the world than bad.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":156790,"text":"But, determined not to let\nthis one incident make me lose faith"},{"time":159813,"text":"in the solidarity in my community\nor humanity as a whole,"},{"time":162550,"text":"I recalled the 7/7 terrorist bombings\nin July 2005 on London transport,"},{"time":167052,"text":"and how the mayor of London at the time,\nand indeed my own parents,"},{"time":170476,"text":"had insisted that we all get back\non the tubes the next day,"},{"time":173347,"text":"so we wouldn't be defined or changed"},{"time":175134,"text":"by those that had made us feel unsafe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177490,"text":"I told my attacker,"},{"time":179740,"text":"\"You've carried out your attack,"},{"time":181313,"text":"but now I'm getting back on my tube."},{"time":184162,"text":"My community will not feel we are unsafe\nwalking home after dark."},{"time":187453,"text":"We will get on the last tubes home,"},{"time":189180,"text":"and we will walk up our streets alone,"},{"time":191038,"text":"because we will not ingrain\nor submit to the idea"},{"time":193398,"text":"that we are putting ourselves\nin danger in doing so."},{"time":196190,"text":"We will continue\nto come together, like an army,"},{"time":198814,"text":"when any member\nof our community is threatened."},{"time":201785,"text":"And this is a fight you will not win.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":205621,"text":"At the time of writing this letter --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":207452,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":208851,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210020,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":212717,"text":"At the time of writing this letter,"},{"time":214461,"text":"I was studying for my exams in Oxford,"},{"time":216340,"text":"and I was working\non the local student paper there."},{"time":218748,"text":"Despite being lucky enough to have\nfriends and family supporting me,"},{"time":222072,"text":"it was an isolating time."},{"time":223304,"text":"I didn't know anyone\nwho'd been through this before;"},{"time":225815,"text":"at least I didn't think I did."},{"time":227283,"text":"I'd read news reports, statistics,\nand knew how common sexual assault was,"},{"time":230801,"text":"yet I couldn't actually name\na single person"},{"time":232882,"text":"that I'd heard speak out\nabout an experience of this kind before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235989,"text":"So in a somewhat spontaneous decision,"},{"time":237950,"text":"I decided that I would publish\nmy letter in the student paper,"},{"time":240970,"text":"hoping to reach out to others in Oxford"},{"time":242902,"text":"that might have had a similar experience\nand be feeling the same way."},{"time":246297,"text":"At the end of the letter,"},{"time":247547,"text":"I asked others to write in\nwith their experiences"},{"time":249937,"text":"under the hashtag, \"#NotGuilty,\""},{"time":251653,"text":"to emphasize that survivors of assault\ncould express themselves"},{"time":254703,"text":"without feeling shame or guilt\nabout what happened to them --"},{"time":257633,"text":"to show that we could all\nstand up to sexual assault."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260233,"text":"What I never anticipated\nis that almost overnight,"},{"time":263089,"text":"this published letter would go viral."},{"time":265619,"text":"Soon, we were receiving\nhundreds of stories"},{"time":268169,"text":"from men and women across the world,"},{"time":269976,"text":"which we began to publish\non a website I set up."},{"time":272672,"text":"And the hashtag became a campaign."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275652,"text":"There was an Australian mother in her 40s\nwho described how on an evening out,"},{"time":279366,"text":"she was followed to the bathroom"},{"time":280946,"text":"by a man who went\nto repeatedly grab her crotch."},{"time":283296,"text":"There was a man in the Netherlands"},{"time":284942,"text":"who described how he was date-raped\non a visit to London"},{"time":287658,"text":"and wasn't taken seriously\nby anyone he reported his case to."},{"time":290564,"text":"I had personal Facebook messages\nfrom people in India and South America,"},{"time":294022,"text":"saying, how can we bring\nthe message of the campaign there?"},{"time":297173,"text":"One of the first contributions we had\nwas from a woman called Nikki,"},{"time":299995,"text":"who described growing up,\nbeing molested my her own father."},{"time":302836,"text":"And I had friends open up to me"},{"time":304343,"text":"about experiences ranging\nfrom those that happened last week"},{"time":307460,"text":"to those that happened years ago,\nthat I'd had no idea about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":311326,"text":"And the more we started\nto receive these messages,"},{"time":313709,"text":"the more we also started\nto receive messages of hope --"},{"time":316317,"text":"people feeling empowered\nby this community of voices"},{"time":318816,"text":"standing up to sexual assault\nand victim-blaming."},{"time":321344,"text":"One woman called Olivia,"},{"time":322667,"text":"after describing how she was attacked"},{"time":324476,"text":"by someone she had trusted\nand cared about for a long time,"},{"time":327326,"text":"said, \"I've read many\nof the stories posted here,"},{"time":329748,"text":"and I feel hopeful that if so many\nwomen can move forward,"},{"time":332762,"text":"then I can, too."},{"time":333968,"text":"I've been inspired by many,"},{"time":335299,"text":"and I hope I can be as strong\nas them someday."},{"time":337516,"text":"I'm sure I will.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":339082,"text":"People around the world began\ntweeting under this hashtag,"},{"time":341832,"text":"and the letter was republished\nand covered by the national press,"},{"time":344933,"text":"as well as being translated into several\nother languages worldwide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348642,"text":"But something struck me\nabout the media attention"},{"time":351040,"text":"that this letter was attracting."},{"time":352675,"text":"For something to be front-page news,"},{"time":354777,"text":"given the word \"news\" itself,"},{"time":357768,"text":"we can assume it must be something new\nor something surprising."},{"time":361172,"text":"And yet sexual assault\nis not something new."},{"time":363870,"text":"Sexual assault, along with other\nkinds of injustices,"},{"time":366755,"text":"is reported in the media all the time."},{"time":369154,"text":"But through the campaign,"},{"time":370376,"text":"these injustices were framed\nas not just news stories,"},{"time":373007,"text":"they were firsthand experiences\nthat had affected real people,"},{"time":376349,"text":"who were creating,\nwith the solidarity of others,"},{"time":378723,"text":"what they needed\nand had previously lacked:"},{"time":380838,"text":"a platform to speak out,"},{"time":382259,"text":"the reassurance they weren't alone\nor to blame for what happened to them"},{"time":385735,"text":"and open discussions that would help\nto reduce stigma around the issue."},{"time":389388,"text":"The voices of those directly affected\nwere at the forefront of the story --"},{"time":393080,"text":"not the voices of journalists\nor commentators on social media."},{"time":396733,"text":"And that's why the story was news."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400239,"text":"We live in an incredibly\ninterconnected world"},{"time":402370,"text":"with the proliferation of social media,"},{"time":404294,"text":"which is of course a fantastic resource\nfor igniting social change."},{"time":407951,"text":"But it's also made us\nincreasingly reactive,"},{"time":410702,"text":"from the smallest annoyances\nof, \"Oh, my train's been delayed,\""},{"time":414113,"text":"to the greatest injustices of war,\ngenocides, terrorist attacks."},{"time":418508,"text":"Our default response has become\nto leap to react to any kind of grievance"},{"time":422030,"text":"by tweeting, Facebooking, hastagging --"},{"time":424202,"text":"anything to show others\nthat we, too, have reacted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427798,"text":"The problem with reacting\nin this manner en masse"},{"time":430135,"text":"is it can sometimes mean\nthat we don't actually react at all,"},{"time":433080,"text":"not in the sense of actually\ndoing anything, anyway."},{"time":435553,"text":"It might make ourselves feel better,"},{"time":437315,"text":"like we've contributed\nto a group mourning or outrage,"},{"time":439890,"text":"but it doesn't actually change anything."},{"time":441876,"text":"And what's more,"},{"time":443064,"text":"it can sometimes drown out the voices"},{"time":444892,"text":"of those directly\naffected by the injustice,"},{"time":447014,"text":"whose needs must be heard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449780,"text":"Worrying, too, is the tendency\nfor some reactions to injustice"},{"time":453657,"text":"to build even more walls,"},{"time":455278,"text":"being quick to point fingers\nwith the hope of providing easy solutions"},{"time":458664,"text":"to complex problems."},{"time":460328,"text":"One British tabloid,\non the publication of my letter,"},{"time":462891,"text":"branded a headline stating,"},{"time":464444,"text":"\"Oxford Student Launches\nOnline Campaign to Shame Attacker.\""},{"time":469567,"text":"But the campaign never\nmeant to shame anyone."},{"time":472237,"text":"It meant to let people speak\nand to make others listen."},{"time":476186,"text":"Divisive Twitter trolls were quick\nto create even more injustice,"},{"time":479624,"text":"commenting on\nmy attacker's ethnicity or class"},{"time":482598,"text":"to push their own prejudiced agendas."},{"time":485381,"text":"And some even accused me\nof feigning the whole thing"},{"time":488866,"text":"to push, and I quote,"},{"time":490996,"text":"my \"feminist agenda of man-hating.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":494834,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":495920,"text":"I know, right?"},{"time":497104,"text":"As if I'm going to be like,\n\"Hey guys! Sorry I can't make it,"},{"time":499993,"text":"I'm busy trying to hate\nthe entire male population"},{"time":502382,"text":"by the time I'm 30.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":503791,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":504953,"text":"Now, I'm almost sure"},{"time":507025,"text":"that these people wouldn't say\nthe things they say in person."},{"time":510021,"text":"But it's as if because they might\nbe behind a screen,"},{"time":512807,"text":"in the comfort in their own home"},{"time":514390,"text":"when on social media,"},{"time":515565,"text":"people forget that what\nthey're doing is a public act --"},{"time":518243,"text":"that other people will be reading it\nand be affected by it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521043,"text":"Returning to my analogy\nof getting back on our trains,"},{"time":524640,"text":"another main concern I have\nabout this noise that escalates"},{"time":527497,"text":"from our online responses to injustice"},{"time":529397,"text":"is that it can very easily slip\ninto portraying us as the affected party,"},{"time":532896,"text":"which can lead to a sense of defeatism,"},{"time":534940,"text":"a kind of mental barrier to seeing\nany opportunity for positivity or change"},{"time":538683,"text":"after a negative situation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541092,"text":"A couple of months\nbefore the campaign started"},{"time":543351,"text":"or any of this happened to me,"},{"time":544816,"text":"I went to a TEDx event in Oxford,"},{"time":546586,"text":"and I saw Zelda la Grange speak,"},{"time":548545,"text":"the former private secretary\nto Nelson Mandela."},{"time":550830,"text":"One of the stories\nshe told really struck me."},{"time":553755,"text":"She spoke of when\nMandela was taken to court"},{"time":555848,"text":"by the South African Rugby Union"},{"time":557462,"text":"after he commissioned\nan inquiry into sports affairs."},{"time":560037,"text":"In the courtroom,"},{"time":561212,"text":"he went up to the South African\nRugby Union's lawyers,"},{"time":564227,"text":"shook them by the hand"},{"time":565411,"text":"and conversed with them,\neach in their own language."},{"time":567878,"text":"And Zelda wanted to protest,"},{"time":569242,"text":"saying they had no right to his respect"},{"time":571173,"text":"after this injustice they had caused him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":573837,"text":"He turned to her and said,"},{"time":576324,"text":"\"You must never allow the enemy\nto determine the grounds for battle.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":581900,"text":"At the time of hearing these words,"},{"time":583634,"text":"I didn't really know why\nthey were so important,"},{"time":585926,"text":"but I felt they were, and I wrote them\ndown in a notebook I had on me."},{"time":589311,"text":"But I've thought about this line\na lot ever since."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592198,"text":"Revenge, or the expression of hatred"},{"time":594739,"text":"towards those who have done us injustice"},{"time":596699,"text":"may feel like a human instinct\nin the face of wrong,"},{"time":599737,"text":"but we need to break out of these cycles"},{"time":601675,"text":"if we are to hope to transform\nnegative events of injustice"},{"time":604807,"text":"into positive social change."},{"time":606906,"text":"To do otherwise"},{"time":608103,"text":"continues to let the enemy\ndetermine the grounds for battle,"},{"time":611406,"text":"creates a binary,"},{"time":612616,"text":"where we who have suffered\nbecome the affected,"},{"time":615144,"text":"pitted against them, the perpetrators."},{"time":618143,"text":"And just like we got back on our tubes,"},{"time":620037,"text":"we can't let our platforms\nfor interconnectivity and community"},{"time":623097,"text":"be the places that we settle for defeat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":627072,"text":"But I don't want to discourage\na social media response,"},{"time":630612,"text":"because I owe the development\nof the #NotGuilty campaign"},{"time":633303,"text":"almost entirely to social media."},{"time":634871,"text":"But I do want to encourage\na more considered approach"},{"time":637420,"text":"to the way we use it\nto respond to injustice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639567,"text":"The start, I think,\nis to ask ourselves two things."},{"time":642042,"text":"Firstly: Why do I feel this injustice?"},{"time":644598,"text":"In my case, there were\nseveral answers to this."},{"time":646928,"text":"Someone had hurt me and those who I loved,"},{"time":649185,"text":"under the assumption they\nwouldn't have to be held to account"},{"time":652109,"text":"or recognize the damage they had caused."},{"time":654046,"text":"Not only that, but thousands\nof men and women suffer every day"},{"time":656978,"text":"from sexual abuse, often in silence,"},{"time":658720,"text":"yet it's still a problem we don't give\nthe same airtime to as other issues."},{"time":662296,"text":"It's still an issue many people\nblame victims for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664840,"text":"Next, ask yourself: How,\nin recognizing these reasons,"},{"time":668146,"text":"could I go about reversing them?"},{"time":670183,"text":"With us, this was holding my attacker\nto account -- and many others."},{"time":673795,"text":"It was calling them out\non the effect they had caused."},{"time":676425,"text":"It was giving airtime\nto the issue of sexual assault,"},{"time":679183,"text":"opening up discussions amongst friends,\namongst families, in the media"},{"time":682568,"text":"that had been closed for too long,"},{"time":684233,"text":"and stressing that victims\nshouldn't feel to blame"},{"time":686614,"text":"for what happened to them."},{"time":687909,"text":"We might still have a long way to go\nin solving this problem entirely."},{"time":691251,"text":"But in this way,"},{"time":692426,"text":"we can begin to use social media\nas an active tool for social justice,"},{"time":695761,"text":"as a tool to educate,\nto stimulate dialogues,"},{"time":697883,"text":"to make those in positions\nof authority aware of an issue"},{"time":700592,"text":"by listening to those\ndirectly affected by it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":704112,"text":"Because sometimes these questions\ndon't have easy answers."},{"time":708606,"text":"In fact, they rarely do."},{"time":710715,"text":"But this doesn't mean we still\ncan't give them a considered response."},{"time":714370,"text":"In situations where\nyou can't go about thinking"},{"time":716598,"text":"how you'd reverse\nthis feeling of injustice,"},{"time":718717,"text":"you can still think,\nmaybe not what you can do,"},{"time":721395,"text":"but what you can not do."},{"time":723681,"text":"You can not build further walls\nby fighting injustice with more prejudice,"},{"time":727397,"text":"more hatred."},{"time":728894,"text":"You can not speak over those\ndirectly affected by an injustice."},{"time":733121,"text":"And you can not react to injustice,\nonly to forget about it the next day,"},{"time":737124,"text":"just because the rest\nof Twitter has moved on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740078,"text":"Sometimes not reacting\ninstantly is, ironically,"},{"time":744289,"text":"the best immediate course\nof action we can take."},{"time":747919,"text":"Because we might be angry, upset\nand energized by injustice,"},{"time":752219,"text":"but let's consider our responses."},{"time":755413,"text":"Let us hold people to account,\nwithout descending into a culture"},{"time":758673,"text":"that thrives off shaming\nand injustice ourselves."},{"time":762345,"text":"Let us remember that distinction,"},{"time":764016,"text":"so often forgotten by internet users,"},{"time":766238,"text":"between criticism and insult."},{"time":769330,"text":"Let us not forget\nto think before we speak,"},{"time":771370,"text":"just because we might\nhave a screen in front of us."},{"time":773811,"text":"And when we create noise on social media,"},{"time":775806,"text":"let it not drown out the needs\nof those affected,"},{"time":778148,"text":"but instead let it amplify their voices,"},{"time":780613,"text":"so the internet becomes a place\nwhere you're not the exception"},{"time":783579,"text":"if you speak out about something\nthat has actually happened to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":786771,"text":"All these considered\napproaches to injustice"},{"time":788848,"text":"evoke the very keystones\non which the internet was built:"},{"time":792317,"text":"to network, to have signal, to connect --"},{"time":794596,"text":"all these terms that imply\nbringing people together,"},{"time":797112,"text":"not pushing people apart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799443,"text":"Because if you look up the word\n\"justice\" in the dictionary,"},{"time":803977,"text":"before punishment,"},{"time":805267,"text":"before administration of law\nor judicial authority,"},{"time":809529,"text":"you get:"},{"time":810799,"text":"\"The maintenance of what is right.\""},{"time":813794,"text":"And I think there are few things\nmore \"right\" in this world"},{"time":817584,"text":"than bringing people together,"},{"time":819344,"text":"than unions."},{"time":821395,"text":"And if we allow social media\nto deliver that,"},{"time":823916,"text":"then it can deliver a very powerful\nform of justice, indeed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":828477,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":829730,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}